00:40:22,290 --> 00:40:24,830
- What's going on here?<br/>- ...custos regne...

521
00:40:24,920 --> 00:40:28,750
I cannot follow you.<br/>I'm confused and I don't understand...

522
00:40:28,840 --> 00:40:31,760
It's the Order<br/>of the Council of State, sir.

523
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:36,050
So that we may act on your behalf...

524
00:40:36,140 --> 00:40:38,100
...much clearer to me, I'm afraid...

525
00:40:40,430 --> 00:40:44,730
- Well, I'm so confused that...<br/>- Approved.

526
00:40:44,810 --> 00:40:46,440
Thank you.

527
00:40:55,110 --> 00:40:58,830
- [Man] Let me help you, sir.<br/>- Ah, yes...

528
00:41:03,750 --> 00:41:06,040
- Thank you, sir.<br/>- Thank you.

529
00:41:11,260 --> 00:41:13,670
- Feeling a little better, sir?<br/>- No, I'm not feeling any better.

530
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:17,050
I feel dreadful. Ah...

