537
00:41:48,210 --> 00:41:51,250
Nor making our own drowsies either,<br/>as we've had to do too often lately.

538
00:41:51,340 --> 00:41:54,170
- [Bertie] David. Dinner.<br/>- I'm on with Wallis.

539
00:41:54,260 --> 00:41:55,970
It's Bertie.

540
00:41:57,300 --> 00:42:00,430
No. No, it's not important.

541
00:42:00,890 --> 00:42:04,060
[Groans]<br/>I don't want to.

