545
00:42:22,030 --> 00:42:25,950
She forgets Papa's bloody clocks<br/>are all half an hour fast.

546
00:42:41,140 --> 00:42:44,560
How's the King?<br/>I... I hope he's not in pain.

547
00:42:44,640 --> 00:42:47,430
