570
00:45:54,660 --> 00:45:56,250
- Dad?<br/>- Mmm-hmm?

571
00:45:56,330 --> 00:45:58,670
- [Man] When he died...<br/>- Time for a Shake, Dad?

572
00:45:58,750 --> 00:46:00,790
