00:46:31,530 --> 00:46:33,790
Art thou afeard?

578
00:46:33,870 --> 00:46:36,250
- Be not afeard.<br/>- Caliban.

579
00:46:36,870 --> 00:46:40,420
Oh, for heaven's sake.<br/>That was a lucky guess.

580
00:46:40,500 --> 00:46:43,040
