581
00:46:43,130 --> 00:46:46,760
The isle is full of noises,<br/>sounds and sweet airs

582
00:46:46,840 --> 00:46:49,090
that give delight, and hurt not.

583
00:46:49,180 --> 00:46:53,180
Sometimes a thousand twangling<br/>instruments will hum about mine ears,

584
00:46:53,260 --> 00:46:57,350
and sometimes voices, that,<br/>if then I had waked after long sleep,

585
00:46:57,430 --> 00:47:01,150
