00:50:07,120 --> 00:50:11,170
- I'm not going to sit here warbling.<br/>- You can with me.

630
00:50:11,250 --> 00:50:14,670
- Because you're peculiar.<br/>- I take that as a compliment.

631
00:50:15,840 --> 00:50:17,380
Well...

632
00:50:18,840 --> 00:50:20,890
Rules are rules.

633
00:50:24,850 --> 00:50:28,640
