658
00:52:26,390 --> 00:52:28,010
"Buh-buh-buh-Bertie."

659
00:52:29,560 --> 00:52:31,480
Father encouraged it.

660
00:52:31,560 --> 00:52:35,810
Said, "Get it out, boy!"<br/>Said it would make me stop.

