- Any other corrections?<br/>- Knock knees.

668
00:53:08,390 --> 00:53:12,680
[Stammering]<br/>Metal splints were made.

669
00:53:12,770 --> 00:53:15,770
Worn... worn day and night.

670
00:53:17,110 --> 00:53:20,520
