685
00:54:16,460 --> 00:54:22,170
As you... as you can imagine,<br/>caused some stomach problems.

686
00:54:23,170 --> 00:54:24,760
Still.

687
00:54:29,140 --> 00:54:31,720
What about your brother, Johnnie?

688
00:54:32,970 --> 00:54:35,430
